item.description:
We are a group of singles looking to meet new people. Online dating and meeting people with a busy lifestyle such as ours is difficult. Are you in Central, CT and want to meet fun, outgoing and optimistic people? Then join us at Murphy & Scarletti's in Farmington. If you'd like to join us for dinner feel free to do so. We'll be there around 8 pm

There may be a cover if you arrive after 9 pm - generally around $6-$10.

Feel free to give us a call on the cell at 860-614-9367 - Christie or Bryan.
